<p>
We are looking for a Lead Software Engineer to lead our team of engineers at our headquarters in San Francisco, CA. The team is focused on innovation and building APIs with modern technologies that have real value for the world, delivering over 120 million requests per day.</p>
<p>
<br />
As a Lead Software Engineer you will be responsible for leading and working with the team on projects supporting the media business, mentoring engineers, building web applications, web APIs, and a cohesive strategy and architecture for our API tier.</p>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
Responsibilities</p>
<p>
