<p>
<br />
&bull;Optimizing performance of the web server tier, APIs, databases, caching layer, and low-level infrastructure</p>
<p>
<br />
&bull;Interacting with the front-end tier teams and technologies for support and development of the applications</p>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
Requirements</p>
<p>
